When working with TextComponent.of you can use the color in the primary constructor.
What I mean is instead of
TextComponent.of("Text").color(TextColor.WHITE);
you do
TextComponent.of("Text", TextColor.WHITE);
Also, on line 105, why are you using a builder instead of just a simple TextComponent.of()?

